                                                    </span>
                                                </div>
                                        

                                        </div>
                                        <div class="block-contact">
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><h3>Write Us</h3><span><a href="mailto:info@paranda.pk">info@paranda.pk</a></span></li>
                                                <li><h3>Call Us</h3><span>+92314 1234567</span></li>
